════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2ead4); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#b98229; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#191817; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Affordable southern Brisbane with genuine motorway connectivity.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Acacia Ridge occupies an interesting position in the southern Brisbane market. It offers affordability that its immediate neighbours have been losing as Moorooka and Salisbury have repriced, combined with exceptional motorway access that makes the suburb genuinely convenient for both workers and logistics operators. The suburb has a residential core that functions independently of its industrial precinct, and buyers who understand that distinction find genuine value here.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
